      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in impeccable, mint condition and presents exactly as it did on the showroom floor. The exterior paint is absolutely flawless with a deep, mirror-like luster, and the interior is pristine, showing no signs of wear. Every mechanical and electronic component functions perfectly, reflecting a history of meticulous maintenance and climate-controlled storage. This is a rare opportunity to own a truly showroom-quality example that will satisfy even the most discerning collector.",
